            sensor data over <strong class="text-frost-300">Zenoh</strong>,
            a publish-subscribe protocol.
            The control interface accepts <code class="text-frost-300 font-mono">applyTorque</code>
            and <code class="text-frost-300 font-mono">applyMagneticDipole</code> commands,
            allowing the complete EKF pipeline to be stress-tested against simulated sensor
            noise and disturbance torques long before any hardware leaves the ground.
